  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>CreateFrameBuffer</TypeRef> method constructs and returns a new object which implements the <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IFrameBuffer">IFrameBuffer</PageRef>
      interface.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[IFrameBuffer::unique_ptr CreateFrameBuffer();]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Return value">
      <ReturnValue Type="IFrameBuffer!cobalt.graphics.IFrameBuffer">
        A freshly constructed <TypeRef>IFrameBuffer</TypeRef> object, wrapped in a <TypeRef>unique_ptr</TypeRef>.
      </ReturnValue>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
